org.openimaj.feature.local

Interface LocationProvider<L extends Location>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - The type of Location.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LocalFeature<L,T>, LocalFeatureVectorProvider<L,T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FloatLocalFeatureAdaptor, LocalFeatureImpl, QuantisedLocalFeature

    public interface LocationProvider<L extends Location>
    A LocationProvider marks classes that have an associated Location or are capable of producing a Location from their internal state.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
